WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:02.711
- I'm a doctor.
- I don't need a doctor, okay?

00:02.713 --> 00:06.215
What I do need is help flipping
my car back over.

00:06.217 --> 00:07.799
The young woman was driving
the vehicle

00:07.801 --> 00:10.302
and seems to have somehow
come out of it okay.

00:10.304 --> 00:11.786
Her father's on her way.

00:11.788 --> 00:14.556
No, he's, uh...
he's already here.

00:14.558 --> 00:16.842
This information together
with your eye symptoms

00:16.844 --> 00:20.062
and recent kidney stones suggest
a serious condition

00:20.064 --> 00:21.763
called sarcoidosis.

00:21.765 --> 00:24.683
If he dies, it's your fault.

00:25.818 --> 00:27.853
When I first met Divya,

00:27.855 --> 00:29.471
her in a white pantsuit,

00:29.473 --> 00:31.823
me in my skivvies...

00:31.825 --> 00:36.078
[Both laughing, chattering]

00:36.080 --> 00:37.145
Oh, by the way,

00:37.147 --> 00:38.697
I'm on my last day
of pain pills.

00:38.699 --> 00:40.499
I could use a refill.
Of course.

00:40.501 --> 00:41.667
You shouldn't need
a refill yet.

00:41.669 --> 00:43.318
What are you implying?

00:43.320 --> 00:45.003
I'm... I'm uncomfortable
writing another prescription

00:45.005 --> 00:46.455
for opiates again so soon.

00:46.457 --> 00:48.173
Sorry I asked.

00:52.128 --> 00:53.462
I'm just dealing
with a patient, Ev.

00:53.464 --> 00:54.996
I'll see you in a couple hours.

00:54.998 --> 00:56.998
Bye.

00:58.000 --> 01:04.074
